# Render.com:
#   1. Go to your Web Service → Environment
#   2. Add each variable above
#   3. Click "Save Changes" and redeploy

# Vercel:
#   1. Go to Project → Settings → Environment Variables
#   2. Add variables for Production environment
#   3. Redeploy

# GitHub Actions:
